Database notes

Install local psql
  /Applications/Postgres.app/Contents/Versions/9.4/bin//psql

Postgres references:
  Arrays: http://www.postgresql.org/docs/9.1/static/arrays.html
  Data definitions: http://www.postgresql.org/docs/9.4/static/ddl.html
  Serial: http://www.postgresql.org/docs/9.4/static/datatype-numeric.html#DATATYPE-SERIAL


get info about database:
  heroku pg:info --app sniksnak

  === HEROKU_POSTGRESQL_ROSE_URL (DATABASE_URL)
  Plan:        Dev
  Status:      Available
  Connections: 0/20
  PG Version:  9.3.6
  Created:     2015-03-30 11:00 UTC
  Data Size:   6.2 MB
  Tables:      0
  Rows:        0/10000 (In compliance)
  Fork/Follow: Unsupported
  Rollback:    Unsupported

pull into local database:
  heroku db:pull

start postgres console:
  heroku pg:psql

  view tables:
    \d
  view specific table
    \d tablename
  select from table:
    select * from tablename;
  http://www.postgresql.org/docs/9.4/static/app-psql.html

